title: "Funny riddle"
doc: "Given a topic, come up with a list of related funny riddles"
prompt-version: 1
prompt: |+
  Here is a list of funny riddles and jokes:
  ###
  TOPIC: IRISH
  - What do you call a bulletproof Irishman? Rick O'Shea!
  ###
  TOPIC: JOKE
  - What do you call someone with no body and no nose? Nobody knows!
  ###
  TOPIC: COW MOVIES
  - What is a cow's favourite movie? Moo-lan
  ###
  TOPIC: FARMING
  - Why are there no unemployed farmers? They can get a job in any field.
  ###
  TOPIC: SPACE PUN
  - Why do all kids want to be astronauts? Because there is no pressure.
  ###
  TOPIC: BATMAN CHURCH
  - What do you call it when Batman skips church? Christian Bale.
  ###
  TOPIC: <1>
  - <:pp><2>
lm-command: "openai-complete.sh"
model: "davinci"
temperature: 0.8
max-tokens: 60
top-p: 1.0
cache: on
vars:
model: davinci
temperature: 0.8
max-tokens: 60
top-p: 1
best-of: 2
stop-sequences:
- "##"
- "\n"
cache: true
vars:
- topic
- beinning
examples:
- tectonic plates
- What do you call
preprocessors:
- tr '[:lower:]' '[:upper:]'
prefer-external: true
var-defaults:
- "(pen-thing-at-point-ask)"
external-related:
- "https://riddles.net/funny-riddles"
n-test-runs: 10
# This will generate 30 pick up lines
n-collate: 2
n-completions: 15
postprocessor: sed 's/^ *//' | awk 1 | sed '/^[^a-zA-Z]/d'
collation-separator: ''